    "At inference time, a neural network ϵ θ iteratively denoises X T ∼ N (0, I) to obtain X 0.",
    "In text-to-image models, denoising is typically performed in latent space; a VAE decoder D then maps X 0 to pixel space, yielding the final image I 0 = D(X 0).",
